	<key>readme</key>
	<string>Google Image Search workflow for Alfred.

Configure your Google Custom Search JSON API key and Programmable Search Engine ID in the workflow's configuration before use.

Usage:
  images &lt;query&gt;   Search Google Images and view results in Grid View
  Enter            Copy the selected image to the clipboard
  Shift+Enter      Open the direct image URL in your browser
  Cmd+Enter        Copy the direct image URL as text
  Alt+Enter        Open the source page in your browser

See README.md for full setup instructions.</string>
